{
  "stem": "24130.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He says that the women go to-- to shul and they would pray, say Kaddish, for their parents.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was so far removed from us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A girl would never go near a [INAUDIBLE] or pray.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he would tell us different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we knew a lot of things from my father because he traveled a lot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the-- the Germans, we didn't-- we didn't have any connection with the Germans until they occupied the country.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But the Hungarians, they organized the people that lived in the town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Like I said, they organized that was called-- not Hitler Jungen-- it was like Hitler Jugend-- they called them Levente.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And this Levente, boys they were are so hostile to Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They would take the Jewish boys from-- from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They's pull out those kids-- poor kids.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They had to shovel their snow, and they had to clean their boots, and they-- and they used to beat up the Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we were really afraid, like we weren't allowed to go on the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But sometimes if we snuck, we-- were were watching the Levente shun squeal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They were the one that they squeal to the authority on us, the Levente.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And these were boys that went to school with my sisters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were older.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were, let's say, 18, 19 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they belonged to this party.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They called themselves Levente.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they were-- we were so scared of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Saturday we would go to shul.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He's-- one said-- and they would say we have to shake their hand and kiss their hand.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And my father says, I'm going to shul.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I'm not going to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He said, you come tonight and I'll explain you why.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He wasn't afraid of my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he came.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
